overview: The best know and best selling Sorority in porn movie history is back with a fifth installment. The charter pledge class at Nevada Cascade College has been through Hell Week and awaits formal initiation into Upsilon Sigma Sorority. The Sorority? Sex Kittens series has become legendary for the famous first-of-its-kind finishing scenes, but would you rather have one cluttered, elongated orgy for spectacle or two bristling-hot, more manageable raunchfests that provide maximum heat? With SSK-5, the proper choice was made for you...
tagline: You'll Wish You'd Never Left College!
title: Sorority Sex Kittens 5
